Douglas C. Yearley Jr.
Executive Compensation
As Chief Executive Officer at TOLL BROTHERS INC, Douglas C. Yearley Jr. made $11,910,879 in total compensation.  Of this total $1,000,000 was received as a salary, $2,564,588 was received as a bonus, $2,305,908 was received in stock options, $6,003,112 was awarded as stock and $37,271 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


