                                                    Toll Brothers, Inc. Prices $150 Million of Senior Notes
                                                


                                                    GlobeNewswire – 
                                                    6:50 PM ET 06/07/2017
                                                


Toll Brothers, Inc. (TOL), announced today that it has priced an underwritten tack-on offering of an additional $150 million of the 4.875% Senior Notes due March 15, 2027 previously issued by Toll Brothers Finance Corp., a wholly-owned subsidiary of the Company. The Company expects to use the net proceeds from the Offering for general corporate purposes.

















